From: twisti <76837088+twisti-dev@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sat, 16 May 2026 16:47:11 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] update gradle build configuration

* add root build configuration for Kotlin, Dokka, Java library, and Maven publishing
* configure sources, Javadocs, JVM toolchain 25, and release repository publishing
* replace module-local repositories and dependency versions with shared version catalog entries
* limit included modules to Folia and Velocity API and core projects
* update Gradle wrapper from 8.9 to 9.5.1

